name: Cellfish (itch)
description:
A fast-paced game where you play as a cell and try to survive as many waves of incoming bacteria as possible. World record on normal (by me) is level 7. If you beat that you're honestly a genius.

The game is unfinished and will stay that way, since I decided not to renovate my GameMaker licence, but I'm just looking for some feedback. I reckon it's still pretty fun though :) . 

Known bugs:

- Chloroplast (green collectible) doesn't do anything.

- Collecting the Mitochondria (orange collectible) may break animations and block firing.

Made in GameMaker
